Command to create a new folder using serverless CLI command :
-> serverless create --template aws-nodejs --path ServerlessProject
we are using aws, nodejs we ahve template called aws-nodejs
This command has created a template inside the folder (ServerlessProject) mentioned in the path with all serverless code that we need.

Command to deploy : sls deploy 
here,
'sls' is short for serverless

This deploy command will create a serverless config file, a CFT template which will build all the resources and things inside this account, region 
(currently in default region set in configuration).


